{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"NoCoder Blog","author":"Jason Yang"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"69c1797f-d27d-5ef1-be0f-f05eda146660","excerpt":"又偏离航线了，一开始就为了装个黑域，从安装adb到更新homebrew、再到更新ruby，我在瞎折腾的路上无法自拔。。。 大概过程是这样\n首先安装android-platform-tools  \n这玩意就开始更新，看来我确实很久没用homebrew装软件了。 然后蹦出来个这 用rvm来管理ruby版本，所以先把rvm…","html":"<blockquote>\n<p>又偏离航线了，一开始就为了装个黑域，从安装adb到更新homebrew、再到更新ruby，我在瞎折腾的路上无法自拔。。。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>大概过程是这样\n首先安装android-platform-tools <code class=\"language-text\">brew install android-platform-tools</code>\n这玩意就开始更新，看来我确实很久没用homebrew装软件了。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token class-name\">Updating</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Homebrew</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>\n<span class=\"token operator\">==</span><span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Downloading</span> https<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>homebrew<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bintray<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>bottles<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>portable<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>portable<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>ruby<span class=\"token operator\">-</span><span class=\"token number\">2.3</span><span class=\"token number\">.3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>leopard_64<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bottle<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token number\">1.</span>tar<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>gz</code></pre></div>\n<p>然后蹦出来个这</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>usr<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>local<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Homebrew</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Library</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Homebrew</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>brew<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>rb<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token number\">12</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span>in `<span class=\"token generics\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>main<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token string\">': Homebrew must be run under Ruby 2.3! You'</span>re running <span class=\"token number\">2.0</span><span class=\"token number\">.0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token class-name\">RuntimeError</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>用rvm来管理ruby版本，所以先把rvm安装一下，简单3步\n(1)<code class=\"language-text\">curl -L get.rvm.io | bash -s stable</code>\n(2)<code class=\"language-text\">source ~/.profile</code>\n(3)<code class=\"language-text\">source ~/.bash</code></p>\n<p>折腾完看看版本号\n<code class=\"language-text\">rvm -v</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">rvm 1.29.3 (latest) by Michal Papis, Piotr Kuczynski, Wayne E. Seguin [https://rvm.io]</code></pre></div>\n<p>装完rvm，就可以更新ruby了</p>\n<p>可以用<code class=\"language-text\">rvm list known</code>查看一下已发布的版本，我这里安装2.3.4版本</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">rvm install 2.3.4</code></p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">ruby -v</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">ruby 2.3.4p301 (2017-03-30 revision 58214) [x86_64-darwin15]</code></pre></div>\n<p>更新完ruby，再来试试homebrew～</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"java\"><pre class=\"language-java\"><code class=\"language-java\">brew cask install android<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>platform<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>tools\nadb devices\n<span class=\"token class-name\">List</span> of devices attached\n<span class=\"token number\">1164111025</span>\tunauthorized</code></pre></div>\n<p>Game Over！</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"mac osx ruby 升级","date":"2017-11-26 16:23:48"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/mac osx ruby 升级/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/singleton-pattern/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"单例模式"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/change-or-accept/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"不能改变，那就接受"}}}}